Package org.forgerock.openam.session.service

Class SessionAccessManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.forgerock.openam.session.service.SessionAccessManager
  • @Singleton
public class SessionAccessManager
extends Object
    Class for managing access to Sessions. This class handles concepts such as persisting a session for the first time, as well as updating a stored session.
